    "innerText": "Sattanagaresu paññattasikkhāpadavaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "335"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aḍḍhuḍḍhasatānī"
      },
      "ti ",
      " tīṇi satāni paññāsañca sikkhāpadāni. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Viggaha"
      },
      "nti manussaviggahaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Atireka"
      },
      "nti dasāhaparamaṃ atirekacīvaraṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kāḷaka"
      },
      "nti ‘‘suddhakāḷakāna’’nti vuttakāḷakaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bhūta"
      },
      "nti bhūtārocanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paramparabhatta"
      },
      "nti paramparabhojanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bhikkhunīsu ca akkoso"
      },
      "ti ‘‘yā pana bhikkhunī bhikkhuṃ akkoseyya vā paribhāseyya vā’’ti (pāci. 1029) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Antaravāsaka"
      },
      "nti aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā cīvarapaṭiggaṇhanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Rūpiya"
      },
      "nti rūpiyasaṃvohāraṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sutta"
      },
      "nti ‘‘sāmaṃ suttaṃ viññāpetvā tantavāyehī’’ti (pārā. 637) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ujjhāpanake"
      },
      "ti ujjhāpanake khiyyanake pācittiyaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pācitapiṇḍa"
      },
      "nti bhikkhunīparipācitaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cīvaraṃ datvā"
      },
      "ti ‘‘samaggena saṅghena cīvaraṃ datvā’’ti (pāci. 485) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vosāsantī"
      },
      "ti ‘‘bhikkhū paneva kulesu nimantitā bhuñjanti, tatra cesā bhikkhunī’’ti (pāci. 558) vuttapāṭidesanīyaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Giragga"
      },
      "nti ‘‘yā pana bhikkhunī naccaṃ vā gītaṃ vā’’ti (pāci. 834) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Cariyā"
      },
      "ti ‘‘antovassaṃ cārikaṃ careyyā’’ti (pāci. 970) ca, ‘‘vassaṃvutthā cārikaṃ na pakkameyyā’’ti (pāci. 974) ca vuttasikkhāpadadvayaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Chandadānenā"
      },
      "ti pārivāsikena chandadānena."
    ],
    "innerText": "335.Aḍḍhuḍḍhasatānīti tīṇi satāni paññāsañca sikkhāpadāni. Viggahanti manussaviggahaṃ. Atirekanti dasāhaparamaṃ atirekacīvaraṃ. Kāḷakanti ‘‘suddhakāḷakāna’’nti vuttakāḷakaṃ. Bhūtanti bhūtārocanaṃ. Paramparabhattanti paramparabhojanaṃ. Bhikkhunīsu ca akkosoti ‘‘yā pana bhikkhunī bhikkhuṃ akkoseyya vā paribhāseyya vā’’ti (pāci. 1029) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. Antaravāsakanti aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā cīvarapaṭiggaṇhanaṃ. Rūpiyanti rūpiyasaṃvohāraṃ. Suttanti ‘‘sāmaṃ suttaṃ viññāpetvā tantavāyehī’’ti (pārā. 637) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. Ujjhāpanaketi ujjhāpanake khiyyanake pācittiyaṃ. Pācitapiṇḍanti bhikkhunīparipācitaṃ. Cīvaraṃ datvāti ‘‘samaggena saṅghena cīvaraṃ datvā’’ti (pāci. 485) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. Vosāsantīti ‘‘bhikkhū paneva kulesu nimantitā bhuñjanti, tatra cesā bhikkhunī’’ti (pāci. 558) vuttapāṭidesanīyaṃ. Giragganti ‘‘yā pana bhikkhunī naccaṃ vā gītaṃ vā’’ti (pāci. 834) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ. Cariyāti ‘‘antovassaṃ cārikaṃ careyyā’’ti (pāci. 970) ca, ‘‘vassaṃvutthā cārikaṃ na pakkameyyā’’ti (pāci. 974) ca vuttasikkhāpadadvayaṃ. Chandadānenāti pārivāsikena chandadānena."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Pārājikāni cattārī"
      },
      "ti bhikkhunīnaṃ cattāri pārājikāni. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kuṭī"
      },
      "ti kuṭikārasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Kosiya"
      },
      "nti kosiyamissakasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Seyyā"
      },
      "ti anupasampannena sahaseyyasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Khaṇane"
      },
      "ti pathavīkhaṇanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Gaccha devate"
      },
      "ti bhūtagāmasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Siñca"
      },
      "nti sappāṇakaudakasiñcanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Mahāvihāro"
      },
      "ti mahallakavihāro. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Añña"
      },
      "nti aññavādakaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dvāra"
      },
      "nti yāva dvārakosā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sahadhammo"
      },
      "ti sahadhammikaṃ vuccamāno. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Payopāna"
      },
      "nti surusurukārakaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Eḷakalomānī"
      },
      "ti eḷakalomadhovāpanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Patto"
      },
      "ti ūnapañcabandhanapatto. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ovādo"
      },
      "ti bhikkhunupassayaṃ upasaṅkamitvā ovādo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Bhesajja"
      },
      "nti taduttaribhesajjaviññāpanaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Sūcī"
      },
      "ti aṭṭhimayādisūcigharaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Āraññiko"
      },
      "ti ",
      " ‘‘yāni kho pana tāni āraññakāni senāsanānī’’tiādinā (pāci. 570) vuttapāṭidesanīyaṃ ",
      ". ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ovādo"
      },
      "ti ‘‘yā pana bhikkhunī ovādāya vā saṃvāsāya vā na gaccheyyā’’ti (pāci. 1055) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ."
    ],
    "innerText": "Pārājikāni cattārīti bhikkhunīnaṃ cattāri pārājikāni. Kuṭīti kuṭikārasikkhāpadaṃ. Kosiyanti kosiyamissakasikkhāpadaṃ. Seyyāti anupasampannena sahaseyyasikkhāpadaṃ. Khaṇaneti pathavīkhaṇanaṃ. Gaccha devateti bhūtagāmasikkhāpadaṃ. Siñcanti sappāṇakaudakasiñcanaṃ. Mahāvihāroti mahallakavihāro. Aññanti aññavādakaṃ. Dvāranti yāva dvārakosā. Sahadhammoti sahadhammikaṃ vuccamāno. Payopānanti surusurukārakaṃ. Eḷakalomānīti eḷakalomadhovāpanaṃ. Pattoti ūnapañcabandhanapatto. Ovādoti bhikkhunupassayaṃ upasaṅkamitvā ovādo. Bhesajjanti taduttaribhesajjaviññāpanaṃ. Sūcīti aṭṭhimayādisūcigharaṃ. Āraññikoti ‘‘yāni kho pana tāni āraññakāni senāsanānī’’tiādinā (pāci. 570) vuttapāṭidesanīyaṃ . Ovādoti ‘‘yā pana bhikkhunī ovādāya vā saṃvāsāya vā na gaccheyyā’’ti (pāci. 1055) vuttasikkhāpadaṃ."
  },
  {
