        "innerText": "336"
      },
      ".",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ekatiṃsa garukā"
      },
      " nāma ubhato aṭṭha pārājikā, bhikkhūnaṃ terasa, bhikkhunīnaṃ dasa saṅghādisesā. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Aṭṭhettha anavasesā"
      },
      "ti etesu yathāvuttagarukesu sādhāraṇāsādhāraṇavasena aṭṭha pārājikā anavasesā nāma."
    ],
    "innerText": "336.Ekatiṃsa garukā nāma ubhato aṭṭha pārājikā, bhikkhūnaṃ terasa, bhikkhunīnaṃ dasa saṅghādisesā. Aṭṭhettha anavasesāti etesu yathāvuttagarukesu sādhāraṇāsādhāraṇavasena aṭṭha pārājikā anavasesā nāma."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "subhead"
    },
    "innerText": "Asādhāraṇādivaṇṇanā"
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "paranum"
        },
        "innerText": "338"
      },
      ". ‘‘Dhovanañca paṭiggaho’’ti gāthā aṭṭhakathācariyānaṃ. Tattha ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "dhovanañca paṭiggaho"
      },
      "ti aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā cīvaradhovāpanaṃ cīvarapaṭiggahaṇañca. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Koseyya…pe… dve lomā"
      },
      "ti eḷakalomavagge ādito satta sikkhāpadāni vuttāni. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Vassikā"
      },
      "ti vassikasāṭikasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Āraññakena cā"
      },
      "ti sāsaṅkasikkhāpadaṃ vuttaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Paṇīta"
      },
      "nti paṇītabhojanaviññatti. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Ūna"
      },
      "nti ūnavīsativassasikkhāpadaṃ. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Nisīdane ca yā sikkhā, vassikā yā ca sāṭikā"
      },
      "ti nisīdanavassikasāṭikānaṃ pamāṇātikkamo."
    ],
    "innerText": "338. ‘‘Dhovanañca paṭiggaho’’ti gāthā aṭṭhakathācariyānaṃ. Tattha dhovanañca paṭiggahoti aññātikāya bhikkhuniyā cīvaradhovāpanaṃ cīvarapaṭiggahaṇañca. Koseyya…pe… dve lomāti eḷakalomavagge ādito satta sikkhāpadāni vuttāni. Vassikāti vassikasāṭikasikkhāpadaṃ. Āraññakena cāti sāsaṅkasikkhāpadaṃ vuttaṃ. Paṇītanti paṇītabhojanaviññatti. Ūnanti ūnavīsativassasikkhāpadaṃ. Nisīdane ca yā sikkhā, vassikā yā ca sāṭikāti nisīdanavassikasāṭikānaṃ pamāṇātikkamo."
  },
  {
    "tagName": "p",
    "attributes": {
      "name": "class",
      "value": "bodytext"
    },
    "children": [
      "Āpattikkhandhā ceva uposathādīni ca ‘‘pārājikasaṅghādisesā’’tiādinā vibhattattā ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "‘‘vibhattiyo’’"
      },
      "ti vuttāni. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Tevīsati saṅghādisesā"
      },
      "ti bhikkhunīnaṃ āgatāni dasa, bhikkhūnaṃ terasāti tevīsati. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dvecattālīsa nissaggiyā"
      },
      "tiādīsupi eseva nayo. ",
      {
        "tagName": "span",
        "attributes": {
          "name": "class",
          "value": "bld"
        },
        "innerText": "Dvīhi…pe… kiccaṃ ekena sammatī"
      },
      "ti dvīhi vivādādhikaraṇaṃ, catūhi anuvādādhikaraṇaṃ, tīhi āpattādhikaraṇaṃ, ekena kiccādhikaraṇaṃ sammatīti attho."
    ],
    "innerText": "Āpattikkhandhā ceva uposathādīni ca ‘‘pārājikasaṅghādisesā’’tiādinā vibhattattā ‘‘vibhattiyo’’ti vuttāni. Tevīsati saṅghādisesāti bhikkhunīnaṃ āgatāni dasa, bhikkhūnaṃ terasāti tevīsati. Dvecattālīsa nissaggiyātiādīsupi eseva nayo. Dvīhi…pe… kiccaṃ ekena sammatīti dvīhi vivādādhikaraṇaṃ, catūhi anuvādādhikaraṇaṃ, tīhi āpattādhikaraṇaṃ, ekena kiccādhikaraṇaṃ sammatīti attho."
  },
